subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The main project output will be developed capacity in MED for coordination and monitoring of SPPRSD based on competent staff trained in data collection and analysis and able to assess progress against results-based indicators and to advise on results-oriented target setting.
subproject.title: SPPRSD/MDG Monitoring
